" TERM REMAPS
"
" create a term with powershell in a new tab

nmap <leader>term :ToggleTerm direction=tab<CR>
nmap <leader>ht :ToggleTerm direction=horizontal<CR>
nmap <leader>ft :ToggleTerm direction=float<CR>
nmap <leader>vt :ToggleTerm direction=vertical size=70<CR>
nmap <leader>tt :ToggleTermToggleAll<CR>
